With her tight young body and totally uninhibited sexuality, it's no wonder why she wanted to capture this moment in time. And now you can too!
tagline: Controversial MTV Star Farrah Abraham is Featured in Explicit Private Tape Now Made Public!
title: Farrah Superstar: Backdoor Teen Mom
